## Feature Flag

### `user_limits.use_code_engine` (boolean, default `false`)
- `false` = All traffic routes to n8n (current behavior)
- `true` = All traffic routes to Code Engine
- `draining_to_code` = Dual routing phase (new conversations go to Code Engine, active conversations drain in n8n)

