## Phase 3: Build the Executor Functions & Follow-up Scheduler

### 3A. Master Router
#### [MODIFY] [execute-automation/index.ts](file:///c:/QuickRevert/app.quickrevert.tech/supabase/functions/execute-automation/index.ts)
Lightweight router that receives event and `activity_id`, resolves the matched automation, updates the activity log with the matched `automation_id`, and delegates to the appropriate executor:
- `execute-post-comment`
- `execute-dm`
- `execute-story`

### 3B. Post Comment Executor
#### [NEW] `execute-post-comment/index.ts`
- Reply to the comment using round-robin picker.
- Send DM (supports Text, Buttons, or Carousel Card formatting).
- **Carousel Support**: Format `carouselCards` into FB generic template structure.
- **Schedule Follow-up**: If a follow-up action is active, write a record to `scheduled_followups`.

### 3C. DM / Conversation Menu Executor
#### [NEW] `execute-dm/index.ts`
- Reply with text, template, or Carousel Card.
- **State Machine**: Read/Write state to `contacts.metadata.conversation_state`.
- **Menu Flow**: Recursively handle button postback payloads by matching them against action card IDs, returning child cards dynamically.
- **Complete Flow**: If lead collection succeeds, update pending follow-ups for this `contact_id` + `automation_id` to `'cancelled'`.

### 3D. Story Reply Executor
#### [NEW] `execute-story/index.ts`
- Handle story replies and delegate message execution.

### 3E. Background Follow-up Processor
#### [NEW] `send-scheduled-followups/index.ts`
- Cron-triggered Edge Function running every 5 minutes.
- Fetches all pending follow-ups where `send_at <= NOW()`.
- Sends the messages via Meta Graph API and updates status to `'sent'`.

